Description:
  TheCommentsBase: generators will copy files to install TheComments 3.0 into your App

  Usage: [bundle exec] rails g the_comments_manager OPTION_NAME
  Usage: [bundle exec] rails g the_comments_manager:views OPTION_NAME

# MIGRATIONS::
  > rake the_comments_manager_engine:install:migrations

# This text:
  > rails g the_comments_manager --help

# Main generators:
  > rails g the_comments_manager install

  This will create:
    app/controllers/concerns/the_comments_manager/actions.rb

# Controller generators:
  > rails g the_comments_manager controllers

  This will create:
    app/controllers/concerns/the_comments_manager/actions.rb

# Locales generators:
  > rails g the_comments_manager locales

  This will generate:
    config/locales/en.the_comments_manager.yml
    config/locales/ru.the_comments_manager.yml

# All generators:
  > rails g the_comments_manager all

  This will create:
    app/models/comment.rb
    app/controllers/comments_controller.rb
    config/initializers/the_comments_manager.rb
    config/locales/en.the_comments_manager.yml
    config/locales/ru.the_comments_manager.yml

# View Generators:
  > rails g the_comments_manager:views js
  > rails g the_comments_manager:views assets
  > rails g the_comments_manager:views views
  > rails g the_comments_manager:views all
